response.original_title: Extremely Dangerous Women of Wrestling, Vol. 2
response.overview: By popular demand we bring you the second edition of Extremely Dangerous Women of Wrestling. Witness what started in banquet rooms, fire halls and nightclubs on the East Coast as the Dangerous Women of Wrestling deliver a truly dysfunctional Wrestling experience. From former WWE, ECW and WCW stars to their homegrown strippers turned wrestlers the Dangerous Women of Wrestling action is NON-STOP! The Dangerous Women of Wrestling stopped at nothing to entertain their rabid audiences with crazy extreme matches featuring all kinds of dysfunctional matches that included TABLES, LADDERS, CHAIRS, FIRE and BLOOD! The Dangerous Women of Wrestling were "Beyond Dysfunctional" before it was cool to be "Extreme"!
response.tagline: Welcome to the World of Hardcore Women's Wrestling
response.title: Extremely Dangerous Women of Wrestling, Vol. 2
